      "versionNonce": 560,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1710700000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Logistic Model:\n  P(A wins) = 1 / (1 + 10^(-diff / sigma))\n  sigma = 3.40 (calibrated via backtest)\n\nBayesian Blend:\n  85% model probability\n  + 15% historical seed base rate\n\nRound Amplification (favorites edge):\n  R64: 1.00x  R32: 1.02x  S16: 1.05x\n  E8: 1.08x   F4: 1.10x   Champ: 1.12x",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "r_42",
      "originalText": "Logistic Model:\n  P(A wins) = 1 / (1 + 10^(-diff / sigma))\n  sigma = 3.40 (calibrated via backtest)\n\nBayesian Blend:\n  85% model probability\n  + 15% historical seed base rate\n\nRound Amplification (favorites edge):\n  R64: 1.00x  R32: 1.02x  S16: 1.05x\n  E8: 1.08x   F4: 1.10x   Champ: 1.12x",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
