      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Calibrates sigma parameter\n13 years tested (excl 2020)\n\nAvg R64 accuracy: 73.7%\nRange: 62.5% - 87.5%\n\nBest: 2017 (87.5%)\n      2014, 2025 (81.2%)\nWorst: 2024 (62.5%)\n\nTarget: 72-76%  [MET]",
