      "originalText": "BRACKET SIMULATION ENGINE\n\n  First Four: 4 play-in games\n    --> R64: 32 games (4 regions x 8)\n      --> R32: 16 games\n        --> Sweet 16: 8 games\n          --> Elite Eight: 4 games\n            --> Final Four: 2 games\n              --> Championship: 1 game\n\n  Total: 67 games | Winners feed forward each round",
