      "text": "Check Seed Thresholds:\n\n  R64  5v12: prob >= 40%, diff < 1.2 std\n  R64  6v11: prob >= 44%\n  R64  7v10: prob >= 46%\n  R64  4v13: prob >= 38%, diff < 0.8 std\n  R32  all:  prob >= 46%, diff < 0.8 std\n  S16+ all:  prob >= 49%, gap >= 3 seeds\n\nBudget caps: R64:4  R32:2  S16:1  E8:1",
