      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "DARK HORSES (underseeded)\n\nVanderbilt (5): KADJ 27.5 = 2-seed level\n  EXP 2.31, elite neutral performance\nSt. John's (5): KADJ D 94.2 (elite D)\n  EXP 2.30, Pitino PASE +2.6\nTennessee (6): KADJ 26.0 + D 95.0\n  Underseeded, composite beats Virginia\nIowa (9): KADJ 22.4 > Clemson 19.2\n  9-seed analytically BETTER than 8\nUtah St. (9): ELO rank #14 (!)\n  Model favors over Villanova (8)\nHouston (2): #6 composite as 2-seed\n  Beats Florida (1) in E8 on data",
